 circulate freely. Secure Varoma lid and steam <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Remove Varoma and set aside."},{"content":"Drain lentils through simmering basket. Add drained lentils to mixing bowl and cook <b>7 min\/100°C\/\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Transfer steamed eggplant slices into the base of prepared casserole dish, then top with lentil mixture. Clean and dry mixing bowl."},{"content":"Place butter, milk and flour into mixing bowl and cook <b>8 min\/90°C\/speed 4<b>."},{"content":"Add 60 g of the reserved Parmesan and mix <b>5 sec\/speed 4<b>."},{"content":"Transfer cheese sauce into casserole dish and sprinkle with remaining reserved Parmesan. Bake for 30 minutes (200°C) or until top is lightly golden brown. Cut moussaka into squares and serve hot."}],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","3h 30m","6 portions"]}